哈佛有一项从1991年开始的未来气候变更研究，该研究基于观察，关于土壤碳反馈，这项研究暗示到2100年，地球表层1米的土壤可能释放出的碳多达1900亿吨，这相当于过去二十年燃烧化石燃料排放出的温室气体总量，这是因为温度升高改变了微生物群落。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/energy-environment/wp/2017/10/05/one-of-the-oldest-climate-change-experiments-has-led-to-a-troubling-conclusion|title=One of the oldest climate change experiments has led to a troubling conclusion|last=Mooney|first=Chris|date=2017-10-05|newspaper=The Washington Post|access-date=|archive-date=2019-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190110021240/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/energy-environment/wp/2017/10/05/one-of-the-oldest-climate-change-experiments-has-led-to-a-troubling-conclusion/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|url=http://science.sciencemag.org/content/358/6359/101|title=Long-term pattern and magnitude of soil carbon feedback to the climate system in a warming world|last=Melillo|first=J.M.|last2=Frey|first2=S.D.|journal=Science|publication-date=6 October 2017|bibcode=2017Sci...358..101M|doi=10.1126/science.aan2874|access-date=|last3=DeAngelis|first3=K.M.|last4=Werner|first4=W.J.|last5=Bernard|first5=M.J.|last6=Bowles|first6=F.P.|last7=Pold|first7=G.|last8=Knorr|first8=M.A.|last9=Grandy|first9=A.S.|archive-date=2019-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190124085802/http://science.sciencemag.org/content/358/6359/101|dead-url=no}}</ref>气候模型没有考虑这些可能的反馈机制。另一项哈佛的研究暗示因为温度升高，注入到[[平流层|平流层]]的水蒸气增多，这加剧了[[臭氧|臭氧]]消耗，以后会增加[[皮肤癌|皮肤癌]]的发生几率并会伤害农作物。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2012/07/concerns-about-climate-change-health/|title=Concerns about climate change, health|publisher=Harvard University|year=2012|accessdate=2018-12-31|archive-date=2019-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190207140400/https://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2012/07/concerns-about-climate-change-health/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

北极的温升幅度几乎是世界其它地区的2倍。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://archive.ipcc.ch/publications_and_data/ar4/wg1/en/tssts-3-1-2.html |title=TS.3.1.2 Spatial Distribution of Changes in Temperature, Circulation and Related Variables – AR4 WGI Technical Summary |accessdate=2018-12-30 |archive-date=2018-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181223121212/https://archive.ipcc.ch/publications_and_data/ar4/wg1/en/tssts-3-1-2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>这似乎既是因为极地强化热量传输，更因为当地的净辐射平衡。<ref name="Alexeev">{{cite journal | author = Alexeev V. A., Langen P. L., Bates J. R. | year = 2005 | title = Polar amplification of surface warming on an aquaplanet in "ghost forcing" experiments without sea ice feedbacks | url = | journal = Climate Dynamics | volume = 24 | issue = 7–8| pages = 655–666 | doi=10.1007/s00382-005-0018-3| bibcode = 2005ClDy...24..655A}}</ref>一些能想到的反馈例子包括雪和海冰覆盖面积的减少，大气和海洋环流的变化，北极环境中的人为烟尘，云量增加和水蒸发。根据政府间气候变化专门委员会2013年的报告，模型经常倾向于低估北极强化现象。<ref name="IPCC 2013">{{cite journal|url=http://www.climatechange2013.org/images/report/WG1AR5_Chapter11_FINAL.pdf|title=IPCC AR5 – Near-term Climate Change: Projections and Predictability (Chapter 11 / page 983 )|year=2013|journal=|access-date=2018-12-31|archive-date=2019-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191220024626/http://www.climatechange2013.org/images/report/WG1AR5_Chapter11_FINAL.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://climate.nasa.gov/news/927/arctic-amplification|title=Arctic amplification|work=NASA|year=2013|accessdate=2018-12-31|archive-date=2018-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180731054007/https://climate.nasa.gov/news/927/arctic-amplification/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>一些研究将快速变暖的北极与消失的[[冰雪圈|冰雪圈]]、中纬度地区的极端天气<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1029/2012GL051000 | bibcode=2012GeoRL..39.6801F | volume=39 | title=Evidence linking Arctic amplification to extreme weather in mid-latitudes | year=2012 | journal=Geophysical Research Letters | author=Francis Jennifer A}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal
